    <item>
      <title>英国无家可归者让住房问题成为选民关注的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/rising-uk-homelessness-keeps-housing-crunch-in-front-of-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国无家可归人口激增已成为住房危机的另一个症状，住房危机在下个月大选之前将这一问题推上了政治议程，活动人士表示，主要政党在提供可负担住房方面做得不够。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/rising-uk-homelessness-keeps-housing-crunch-in-front-of-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将抨击法国预算赤字，给马克龙的困境雪上加霜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/eu-to-slam-france-over-budget-deficit-adding-to-political-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在立法选举开始前不到两周，欧盟将对法国违反欧盟赤字和债务规则进行谴责，此举可能导致高额罚款，并使竞选重点复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/eu-to-slam-france-over-budget-deficit-adding-to-political-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
